reviews.review_text: GD in Atlanta Show is from 3/29/89, NOT 1987.  This show is from Atlanta.  3/29/87 is from the Spectrum in Philadelphia w/ completely different setlist.  (Attached Text document is correct)

03-27-89 is the correct date... Mon. 1st night of 3 night run Nope... it's 03-27-89 Atlanta... by the way,  it's the only set 1 closer of Touch of Grey ... I think? It was most common as a set 1 opener , 2nd set opener and or encore ...
